  "helpTitle": "Help",
  "helpQuickStart": "Quick start",
  "helpStepShopsBuyersTitle": "Add shops & buyers",
  "helpStepShopsBuyersDesc": "In Settings, add your sources and buyers. Both are required when creating a deal.",
  "helpStepFirstDealTitle": "Create your first deal",
  "helpStepFirstDealDesc": "Tap \"New deal\" at the bottom. The product field suggests previous products as you type.",
  "helpStepStatsTitle": "Statistics & goals",
  "helpStepStatsDesc": "The Statistics tab shows cashflow, profit and VAT quarters. Set a monthly profit goal in Settings.",
  "helpDiscordSection": "Discord integration",
  "helpDiscordHowTitle": "How linking works",
